### Error Handling

Restart processes or see log at https://[host/base]/admin/ or with â””â–ªcliâ†µ.

If `router`, `log`, `dashboard` or `ci` are affected, use â””â–ªcliâ†µ.

If services have unexpected behaviour, use â””â–ªcurlâ†µ

Force stop with â””â–ªkill -9 [pid]â†µ,

